text: Feb unemployment rates ranged from 2.0% in ND to 5.3% in CA.
State GDP in Q4 2023 was higher than in Q4 2022, in real terms, in all states except DE.
RI and VT saw the highest house price growth between Q4 2022 and Q4 2023.
Feb average private weekly earnings in states ranged from $906 in MS to $1,388 in WA.
Total private sector jobs in Feb 2024 were above Feb 2019 levels in 44 states.
Q4 2023 retail real GDP growth over the year ranged from 6% in OR to 14% in FL.
MS’s unemployment rate was 3.1% in Feb 2024. In Feb 2004, it was 5.7%.
Leisure and hospitality jobs in Feb 2024 were below Feb 2023 levels in 44 states and DC.
HI housing prices reached a decade low in Q4 2023.
